This paper deals with a privacy issue related to targeted advertising, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also involves data collection and analysis, which can be categorized under information retrieval (cs.IR) and social and information networks (cs.SI). The use of Google Display Network and AdWords suggests that the paper may also fall under multimedia (cs.MM) and cybernetics (cs.CY) categories.
